      "summary": "Contract registry assembly is duplicated across sibling modules, creating a coupling hotspot and drift risk.",
      "related_files": [
        "goseg/protocol/contracts/protocol_contracts.go",
        "goseg/protocol/contracts/startram_contracts.go"
      ],
      "evidence": [
        "Both files duplicate the same lifecycle primitives: catalog entry vars, `...ContractCatalogSpecs` slice, and two accessor functions returning copied/snapshotted entries.",
